Install OpenShift  service mesh 3.0 operator.

oc create ns istio-system
oc create ns istio-cni


Install istioCNI  (via operator)
Install istio (via operator)

To enable stric mtls mode:

apiVersion: security.istio.io/v1
kind: PeerAuthentication
metadata:
  name: default
  namespace: demo
spec:
  mtls:
    mode: STRICT

kubectl label namespace avi-system istio.io/rev=default
kubectl label namespace demo istio.io/rev=default
